# Pingback Implementation Roadmap & TODO List

This document provides a step-by-step guide to complete the **Pingback** application, based on the requirements in [README.md](file:///home/jaison/code/projects/pingback/README.md) and the current state of the backend and frontend codebases.

---

## 🛠️ Phase 1: Backend Database & Core Model Fixes

The backend currently has several GORM queries with structural bugs (e.g., querying columns that do not exist or incorrect return types).

- [x] **1.1 Fix GORM Repositories**
  - [x] **Project Repository** ([projectRepository.go](file:///home/jaison/code/projects/pingback/server/internal/app/repository/projectRepository.go)):
    - Correct the `Get` method: Fetch projects by `ID` or list all projects belonging to a user (`UserID`), instead of searching by a non-existent `Email` field.
  - [x] **Widget Repository** ([widget.go](file:///home/jaison/code/projects/pingback/server/internal/app/repository/widget.go)):
    - Correct the `Get` method: Fetch widgets by `ID` or `ProjectID`, instead of querying by `Email`.
  - [x] **Feedback Repository** ([feedbackRepository.go](file:///home/jaison/code/projects/pingback/server/internal/app/repository/feedbackRepository.go)):
    - Correct `GetAll` to query `[]model.Feedback` (slice) instead of a single `model.Feedback`.
    - Fix the return type of `GetAll` to return a slice `([]model.Feedback, error)`.
  - [x] **User Repository** ([userRepository.go](file:///home/jaison/code/projects/pingback/server/internal/app/repository/userRepository.go)):
    - Remove the double `.First(&user)` chain in `Get()` which causes query execution issues.

- [x] **1.2 Setup Database Migration**
  - [x] Update `MigrateDB` in [migrate.go](file:///home/jaison/code/projects/pingback/server/pkg/db/migrate.go) to auto-migrate all database models:
    ```go
    err := db.AutoMigrate(
        &model.User{},
        &model.Project{},
        &model.Widget{},
        &model.Feedback{},
    )
    ```
  - [x] Call `db.MigrateDB(db)` inside `main()` in [main.go](file:///home/jaison/code/projects/pingback/server/cmd/server/main.go) right after database initialization.

